# Design Requirements

## Flight Regime
- Low speed UAV
- Cruise speed: 15–25 m/s
- Reynolds number target: 100k–300k

## Wing Goals
- High lift-to-drag ratio
- Lightweight structure
- Smooth morphing surface
- Minimize flow separation

## Constraints
- Wingspan < 2 m
- Must be manufacturable
- Morphing mechanism must not excessively weaken structure
